features: All-In-One Suspension Trainer Kit: Experience a full body workout at home with our Unity Training Co. suspension training straps, that will help you build muscle, burn fat, and enhance mobility.

features: Plan Workout Like a Pro - Perhaps it's the easy to see instructions that makes Grand Basics gym posters the most popular for home fitness and small gyms. Maybe it's the 460+ home exercise options, or even the eye-catching design that’s cleaner than other workout posters. Regardless, just be careful when you stick Grand Basics on your wall, because you might just get in shape faster than you thought!

460+ Exercise Ideas - While we don’t show you how to create a workout, we give you enough exercises in your workout poster set to last forever! In fact, if you choose 5 random exercises every day, you’d have workouts to last for 50 Billion Years (we did the math). Easy to understand for Beginners, but also easy to glance for pros and PT’s to plan out a personal training session or create it on the fly.

Set of 12, Single-Sided, 17" x 27" Posters - Barbell Exercise Poster, Bodyweight Exercise Poster, Dumbbells Poster, Stability Ball Workout Poster, Kettlebell Workout Chart, Medicine Ball Poster, Tension Bands Exercise, Stretching Poster, Suspension Training, Yoga Poster, Foam Roller Exercise Wall Poster plus Muscle Group Gym Poster. A total workout for Beginners to Experts.

Smooth, Eye-Catching Surface - We use 200gsm, 1.5MIL Laminated Paper for your home gym posters. And unlike thick laminated fitness posters, ours are easier to roll up, and easier to flatten so they sit nice and flat on your wall (use 3M adhesive strips). But more importantly, The Color-Block Titles and Color-Coded Design looks clean and tidy in your home gym decor so it’s easier to find what you need.

As Seen in Yoga Journal - If you’re looking for one of the top poster sets according to the number one source for in-depth yoga pose instruction, (and our existing customers), why not try this set now for 30-Days. They’ll arrive pre-rolled, with instructions on how to easily flatten them. And, if you’re not happy you can return for a refund. So, let’s go! Make your home workouts count with Grand Basics.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
THE ULTIMATE TRAINING TOOL 
What is a Bodytorc Suspension Trainer? 
It is a simple resistance training tool that uses your bodyweight and gravity to give you a full body workout. To increase the level of difficulty you simply make the straps longer to increase the angle. 
Who is a Bodytorc Suspension Trainer for? 
Anyone from beginner to elite level athlete who wants the most versatile functional training tool you can buy. 
What exercises can I do? 
Rows, squats, lunges, hip thrusts, presses, biceps curls, tricep extensions, pikes, crunches, hamstring curls, face pulls, planks....literally too many to name. 
Where can I use it? 
Anywhere you can secure it to something strong enough to take your bodyweight, like a door frame, chin up bar, strong wall anchor or tree branch. 
BODYTORC FUNCTIONAL TRAINER - THE PERFECT WORKOUT TOOL 
TRAIN ANYWHERE 
It is so light and easy to setup you can train at home, while travelling or at the park. 
GREAT FOR STRETCHING 
A fantastic stretching tool. Because it moves with your body you can get the deepest stretch to exactly where you want it. 
INCLUDES HANGING AB STRAPS 
This is an absolute killer ab tool. Combine the extension straps with the foot slings and hang from a chin up bar to strengthen and tone your core. No other system has this option. 
ULTRA HIGH QUALITY PARTS 
We only use the best materials. The top carabiner is lockable if required but if not, simply remove and dispose of screw. 
THE HIGHEST QUALITY - NO COMPROMISES 
Designed by the people who use it everyday. 
You can do more with this system than any other on the market. 
No other system has: 
Dual extension arms 
Hanging ab straps
Detachable handles and foot straps
THE MOST VERSATILE SYSTEM YOU CAN BUY 
CAN BE SET UP: 
On a secure wall or ceiling anchor.
On a chin up bar.
On a door (includes custom door anchor).
Around a tree (includes TWO extension arms for the longest system on the market)
Numbered Arms 
The numbered arms make them super quick and easy to adjust and it's great for measuring your progress. 
Exclusive Video Guides 
We have an extensive online library of exercise guides for beginner to advanced users. 
Ultimate Value 
Why pay more for less?

features: Mesh Nylon Strap and foam Handles
Imported

PORTABLE HOME GYM: TRX GO is a lightweight Suspension Trainer that is easy to use as a home workout system or take on the go. It’s easy to pack for travel and perfect for fun, fast, and effective workouts anywhere and anytime in as little as 20 minutes per day.

SEE THE RESULTS: Bodyweight Suspension Training has been proven to increase muscular activation, reduce injury risk, and accelerate results. TRX allows you to build lean muscle, burn fat, increase range of motion, and improve your performance in life and sports.

SAFETY TESTED: TRX is safety tested to support bodyweight up to 700 lbs. TRX has been used for over 10 years by the US Military, Pro Sports teams, and world-class athletes worldwide and comes with our full TRX two-year Superior Quality Warranty.

YOUR TRIAL TO THE TRX TRAINING CLUB APP: Experience unlimited access to 500+ on-demand workouts: weight training, cardio, cross-training, sport athleticism, resistance and mobility training, and prehab and rehab. Find 100s of workouts for every goal! All workouts are guided by world-class certified TRX trainers.
NOTE: You no longer need a Key To Free Card to access our TRX Training Club App. You can download the app and access your free trial.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Tips to Install POWER GUIDANCE Wall Anchor 
You’ll need to prepare a ¼-inch or bit, a stud finder, a ratchet, a pencil. ALWAYS WEAR SAFETY GLASSES.
You’ll need to find a stud in your wall, an overhead stud, or an overhead beam that is 7- to 9-feet off the ground.
If you need to install overhead or on high ceiling, position the mount at least 3 feet away from the nearest wall to allow for 360° movement for training exercises.
Confirm the drill bit size and hole depth. POWER GUIDANCE mount anchor fits 1/4" or 3/8"deep.
What Should You Pay Attention To 
If you’ve never used a drill or a stud finder, or you don’t know the difference between a nail and a screw, please ask help for a pro to ensure the job’s done right.
The POWER GUIDANCE Ceiling Mount Bracket CANNOT be anchored to drywall or plaster. It must be anchored to a stud to support your weight, you can install the resistance band anchor on concrete or wood wall.

title: Home Resistance Training Kit, Suspension Trainer Exercise Straps with Handles for Full-Body Workout with 5 Resistance Bands, 1 Carrying Bag and 1 Door Anchor for Home Gym Equipment or Outdoor Workouts
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Resistance Bands
features: 【ULTRA - EFFICIENT FITNESS】The bodyweight resistance training system is designed to make bodyweight workouts more convenient and challenging while increasing the balance, coordination, and stability of the entire muscle group of the body. With the bodyweight strap, you can perform over 300 strength training, cardio, yoga, and HIIT exercises, providing you with a full-body workout. You can achieve excellent results for building muscle strength, strengthening the core, burning fat, and sculpting curves.

【QUALITY ASSURANCE - SAFETY FIRST】The resistance training strap is made of industrial-strength nylon webbing with high-density threading, firm stitching, and tear resistance. It is also designed with high-quality soft foam-wrapped handles to prevent slipping when sweating and provide a comfortable feel. The hook is made of anti-rust zinc alloy carabiner, which is extremely strong and durable and can bear up to 900 lbs of weight. You don't have to worry about the training strap breaking during use.

【ADJUSTABLE LENGTH, OPTIONAL INTENSITY】The length of the resistance trainer straps can be adjusted between 55.9” and 63.7”. Additionally, with the door anchor installed, the length of bodyweight training straps can reach 83.4”. In addition, the kit also includes 5 extra latex resistance loop bands, each with a different load capacity (5 lbs/10 lbs/20 lbs/30 lbs/40 lbs), you can adjust your training intensity by changing the length of the bodyweight resistance straps and modifying your body posture.

【EXERCISE ANYTIME & ANYWHERE】The bodyweight resistance trainer kit allows you to exercise almost anywhere. You can use it on the door of your home or tie the straps to a tree, pole, or any sturdy and safe object. description: The TRX Training RIP Trainer Resistance Cord is a versatile addition to your workout equipment collection, providing you with a single resistance cord tailored to your fitness level. By attaching one of our weighted resistance cords, you can engage in a comprehensive full-body workout that targets your core, upper body, and lower body. Whether you prefer a light and fast workout or are aiming to build power with heavier resistance, the RIP Trainer Resistance Cord offers a dynamic way to challenge your balance, stability, and strength at your own pace.Move for the things that matter. TRX strength-training equipment is used by beginners, pro athletes, celebrity trainers, runners, yogis, cyclists, cross-trainers, service members, physical therapists, and combat athletes. With the TRX Training Club fitness app, you’ll have unlimited access to a virtual gym that includes live-streaming classes 7 days a week and hundreds of on-demand workouts, and you can even be matched with a personal trainer for a 1:1 training session. You can filter workouts by body part, workout type, duration, trainer, and fitness level. Whether you need yoga, HIIT, cardio, or strength-training equipment, we have what you need, when you need it. Join our loyal worldwide community and transform your entire body today.
features: RESISTANCE WORKOUT EQUIPMENT: This exercise equipment features a single resistance cord. Choose a light, medium, heavy, x-heavy, or xx-heavy resistance rope. It hooks up with our TRX RIP Trainer to offer the right resistance level for you.

PORTABLE WORKOUT EQUIPMENT: The TRX RIP training system is easy to unhook and set up. Attach one of our weighted resistance cords to it to get a full-body workout wherever you are. Train inside, outside, and on the go.

VERSATILE WORKOUT BAR: Choose from a wide variety of workout options to train your upper body, lower body, or core. Build up resistance, tackle cardio, or add lean muscle with a few simple movements a day.

TOTAL-BODY RESISTANCE: Light and fast? Choose the lighter weight. Ramping up power? Go controlled and heavy. Challenge your balance, stability, and strength, all at your own pace. Work your core and upper and lower body with our resistance cords.

YOUR TRIAL TO THE TRX TRAINING CLUB APP: Experience unlimited access to 500+ on-demand workouts: weight training, cardio, cross-training, sport athleticism, resistance and mobility training, and prehab and rehab. Find 100s of workouts for every goal! All workouts are guided by world-class certified TRX trainers.

title: TRX All-in-One Suspension Training System for Weight Training, Cardio, Cross-Training & Resistance Training, Full-Body Workouts for Home, Travel, and Outdoors, Includes Indoor & Outdoor Anchor System
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Suspension Trainers
features: HOME GYM EQUIPMENT: TRX’s All-in-One Suspension Trainer System has revolutionized personal fitness. It’s designed for full-body training workouts anywhere, anytime, using only your bodyweight. The kit includes the All-in-One Suspension Trainer, Indoor/Outdoor Anchors, and a Mesh Travel Bag.

BEYOND GYM STRAPS: This TRX home workout system will allow you to achieve the results you want. You will build muscle, burn fat, strengthen your core, increase cardio endurance, and improve flexibility efficiently to transform the way you look, feel, and think.

WORKOUT ANYWHERE: TRX easily anchors to doors, rafters, or beams at home—as well as to trees, poles, or posts. Take the TRX All-in-One Suspension Training System to the beach, park, hotel, mountain, or anywhere you love to work out.

SAFETY TESTED: TRX is safety tested to support weight up to 700 lbs. TRX has been used for over 10 years by the US Military, Pro Sports teams, and world-class athletes worldwide and comes with our full TRX two-year Superior Quality Warranty.

YOUR TRIAL TO THE TRX TRAINING CLUB APP: Experience unlimited access to 500+ on-demand workouts: weight training, cardio, cross-training, sport athleticism, resistance and mobility training, and prehab and rehab. Find 100s of workouts for every goal! All workouts are guided by world-class certified TRX trainers.
NOTE: You no longer need a Key To Free Card to access our TRX Training Club App. You can download the app and access your free trial.

features: RESISTANCE BANDS FOR WORKING OUT: This TRX Bandit workout-band kit comes with two 5-to-15-pound strength bands, two 15-to-30-pound strength bands, and 2 resistance-band handles that provide extra grip during your workouts for increased comfort and performance.

HOME WORKOUT EQUIPMENT: Each universal-fit handle offers a better grip without any plastic digging into your palm or “hand-to-band” pinching. Attach the resistance bands to the handles to stretch and tone your body anytime.

TOTAL-BODY WORKOUT: Pack and carry this light band workout gear anywhere for on-the-go strength, endurance, and mobility workouts. Use these bands at the gym or yoga studio to increase your flexibility and strength.

PORTABLE GYM: No matter your fitness level, you can always use exercise tools. Our exercise accessories are great for use at the gym or home. Whether you’re a seasoned pro, a beginner, or in between the two, we have the gear to make fit happen.

YOUR TRIAL TO THE TRX TRAINING CLUB APP: Experience unlimited access to 500+ on-demand workouts: weight training, cardio, cross-training, sport athleticism, resistance and mobility training, and prehab and rehab. Find 100s of workouts for every goal! All workouts are guided by world-class certified TRX trainers.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Strength Training with Confidence

Use them for full-body exercises, including rows, bicep curls, squats, and more, to enhance muscle definition and improve overall fitness. Lightweight and portable, they come with a convenient carry bag, making them ideal for workouts on the go. Build your strength and confidence with GODBOD.

In this image, the user demonstrates bicep curls using the yellow resistance band, emphasizing muscle toning and strength training. Perfect for fitness enthusiasts of all levels, this versatile set offers adjustable resistance levels up to 150 lbs, allowing you to customize your training routine. Made from premium, snap-resistant latex, these bands ensure safety and durability during every session. Lightweight and portable, the GODBOD Resistance Bands are ideal for use at home, the gym, or on the go, and the included carry bag makes transportation effortless. Target arms, core, legs, and more with these multifunctional exercise bands designed for strength building, flexibility, and rehabilitation exercises. Whether you're enhancing your fitness or maintaining an active lifestyle, GODBOD helps you achieve your goals with ease and confidence. Elevate your workouts today!

Lightweight and portable, this set includes foam handles, ankle straps, a door anchor, and a carry bag, making it ideal for home, gym, or on-the-go workouts. Use these bands for dips, rows, curls, and to build strength, enhance muscle definition, and achieve your fitness goals. Whether you're aiming for a toned physique or serious muscle gains, GODBOD has you covered. Take the first step toward peak performance today! 
Durable Design You Can Trust 
Enhance your arm strength and muscle tone with the GODBOD Resistance Bands Set, the ideal fitness tool for targeted workouts. In this image, the user performs resistance band curls indoors, emphasizing arm and bicep development while showcasing the ergonomic foam handles for maximum comfort. Designed for all fitness levels, these bands allow you to customize your resistance, with levels ranging up to 150 lbs, ensuring a personalized workout experience. Made with premium, snap-resistant latex, these bands are built for durability and safety during intense training sessions. Perfect for home workouts or portable enough for use at the gym or on the go, the GODBOD Resistance Bands come with accessories like ankle straps, a door anchor, and a carry bag for added versatility. From strength training to muscle toning, this multifunctional set is your go-to solution for achieving your fitness goals. Build strength, improve flexibility, and enhance your overall fitness with GODBOD today! 
GODBOD Resistance Bands vs Competitors – The Clear Winner in Strength, Accuracy, and Durability 
See why GODBOD Resistance Bands outperform the competition. With 150 lbs of reinforced resistance, our bands deliver unmatched strength compared to competitors' 100 lbs. Unlike other brands with vague indicators, ours feature clearly labeled weight markings for seamless adjustments during workouts. Made from 100% premium latex, GODBOD bands ensure long-term durability, unlike cheap TPU alternatives that break easily. Perfect for home workouts, strength training, and physical therapy, GODBOD bands combine performance, reliability, and safety. Choose GODBOD and experience the ultimate resistance band set designed for results that last. Build strength, tone muscles, and enhance your fitness journey today. Plus, our set includes everything you need: handles, ankle straps, a door anchor, and a carry bag, so you can work out anytime, anywhere. Make the smarter choice and upgrade your workouts now! 
Engineered for Durability, Precision, and Performance 
Discover the superior construction of GODBOD Resistance Bands, designed to deliver unmatched durability and safety. Made from 100% natural latex, these bands provide consistent elasticity and long-lasting performance for intense workouts. Each band features clearly labeled resistance markings, ensuring precise weight adjustments during strength training. The reinforced connections and high-quality metal carabiners enhance stability and security, making them ideal for a wide range of exercises. Unlike inferior alternatives, GODBOD bands are crafted to withstand heavy use without snapping or wearing out. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced athlete, GODBOD Resistance Bands are built to support your fitness goals with reliability and precision. Choose GODBOD and feel the difference in performance and quality today. 
About GODBOD 
At GODBOD, we believe that fitness is a journey that empowers individuals to reach their full potential. Founded by Joseph Maimon, our mission is to provide high-quality, innovative fitness equipment designed to enhance every workout experience. Our journey began when Joseph discovered his passion for fitness after his first gym visit in 2022, leading to a profound sense of pride and fulfillment. 
During a skiing trip in Utah with friends in March 2023, Joseph faced a major setback when he dislocated his shoulder. While navigating a challenging closed tree trail, his friend quickly popped it back in place, but the incident cut his trip short. Opting for a natural recovery, he returned to the gym and resumed lifting, feeling stronger than ever. 
Fast forward to March 2024, while performing military shoulder presses, he heard a loud pop—his shoulder had dislocated again. This time, surgery was unavoidable. The entire experience inspired Joseph to create effective, reliable fitness tools that support others on their journeys, especially during times of recovery and growth. 
Our flagship product, the long resistance bands, is crafted from premium, high-density latex to ensure durability and versatility. With five customizable resistance levels, they cater to users of all fitness levels, making workouts accessible and effective. 
Join the GODBOD community and experience the difference that quality equipment can make in your fitness journey. Together, let’s build strength, resilience, and a healthier lifestyle!

features: PROTECTIVE DOOR: Both ends of the door hook fixing door have added plastic protection pads to help prevent scratching and denting of your door.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Full-body workout? 
THYSOL Resistance Trainer Pro Xtreme Straps 
Inspired by TRX, the suspension trainer is an easy way to train your whole body while working on your balance. Its design makes it easy to use and even easier to store. 
A versatile suspension trainer 
Previous page
Fast, Fun, and Easy 
Train from anywhere 
Easy to adjust 
Includes door anchor 
Ergonomic Grip 
Bring the gym to your home 
Next page
Unlock your full potential in every workout 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
How to hang the suspension trainer 
The door anchor 
Only use the suspension trainer on the side where the door slams shut. This prevents the door from becoming warped and is also less dangerous if someone accidentally opens the door while you are in the middle of an exercise. Preparing your suspension trainer for use with the door anchor is very easy: hang the weighted part of the door anchor over the door and close the door. Then attach the suspension trainer to the anchor with the hook and you’re done! Always check the firmness of the anchorage by pulling firmly on the suspension trainer a few times. 
The suspension anchor 
The suspension anchor is the loose yellow ribbon with black seams on it that comes with the suspension trainer. You would think that the different pockets of the suspension anchor are meant to insert the hook of the suspension trainer itself so that you can easily adjust the height. This is not true! Place the hook of the suspension trainer in the lower loop of the suspension anchor. If you do anchor the suspension trainer in the other compartments, the seams can tear out, which can lead to you falling while hanging with your full weight on the suspension trainer. This can lead to nasty injuries or even worse. The pockets in the suspension anchor are intended to hold the hook of the suspension anchor itself. Use the suspension anchor as attachment around, for example, a tree or post. Wrap the anchor around the object as often as possible and fix the hook in one of the previously mentioned pockets. You can also use the hook of the suspension anchor as a loop.

features: All-in-One Portable Gym for Full Body Workouts:This bodyweight resistance training kit is perfect for home workouts, allowing you to train anywhere with the door anchor and adjustable straps. Set it up easily on doors, beams, trees, or other sturdy objects. Ideal for indoor or outdoor fitness, this versatile resistance training system targets all muscle groups, including arms, legs, chest, back, and core.

Premium Quality and Durability:Our resistance training equipment is crafted with heavy-duty materials and fourfold stitching, ensuring durability. Designed to support up to 550 pounds of bodyweight, the non-slip handles provide a comfortable, secure grip for a superior workout experience.

Full Body Strength and Resistance Training:This fitness resistance kit is suitable for all fitness levels, helping you achieve any fitness goal—whether building muscle, burning fat, or increasing endurance. Perform a variety of exercises, including push, pull, squat, lunge, and more, for a comprehensive full-body workout. Perfect for home gym enthusiasts or personal trainers.

Easy Setup and Versatile Use:Designed for convenience, this portable resistance trainer is easy to set up and adjust with its simple buckle system. Use the door anchor or attach it to horizontal bars, railings, or trees for a quick, effective workout anytime, anywhere. Great for aerial yoga and various strength training routines.

Complete Home Gym Resistance Kit:This portable workout equipment includes everything you need for resistance training: 1 bodyweight training strap, 2 extension straps, 2 exercise bands with handles, 1 door anchor, and a travel bag. Skip the gym fees and enjoy a full-body workout in the comfort of your own space with this versatile, premium fitness system.
Premium Support:If you experience any issues with our home resistance training kit, contact us via your order details or email. Our team will resolve your problem within 24 hours.

features: The Anchor Gym H1 (single unit) provides the platform for hundreds of exercises using resistance bands, body weight straps and stretch straps. Purchase one or outfit an entire fitness area for group training.

The H1 is designed to safely anchor resistance bands, body weight straps, stretch straps and more. It's easy to use, delivers hundreds of great exercises, takes up zero floor space and is very affordable.

EASY TO USE: With the patented open-faced design of its T-bar safety hook, the Anchor Gym makes transitions between exercises as easy as looping and pulling. No need for cumbersome clip hooks, carabineer’s, or fasteners. STRONG AND RELIABLE: Made of solid steel components, the Anchor Gym is a space-saving powerhouse capable of supporting up to 800 pounds of resistance.

INSTALLATION: Wood mounting hardware included. For concrete or block walls use 5 /16” (diameter) x 2.5” (length) sleeve anchors (not included). Detailed installation instructions are included in the Digital Owner's Manual on Page 13. Note: To avoid over torquing and breaking a bolt, drill a 1/4” diameter pilot hole, 2.5” deep. To avoid stripping, do not over tighten bolts.
SATISFACTION GUARANTEED: We believe, you will love the Anchor Gym H1. Backed by a 100% lifetime warranty and satisfaction guarantee! Accessories not included.

HOME GYM EQUIPMENT: The TRX Tactical Gym is our most rugged strap-suspension-trainer kit for the most extreme conditions. It is designed to help military athletes at any level reach their fitness goals and stay mission-ready.

TOTAL-BODY WORKOUT: Whether you’re looking for strength training, cardio, core training, or recovery, the TRX Tactical fitness equipment offers a transformative total-body workout in just 15 minutes a day with 7 simple, functional movements.

PORTABLE GYM: The durable TRX bands in this functional trainer kit are quick to set up and come equipped to help you exercise inside, outside, and on the go. Never miss a workout, no matter where your mission takes you.

NOTE: You no longer need a Key To Free Card to access our TRX Training Club App. You can download the app and access your free trial.

title: TRX Training XMount, Training Anchor Mount for Suspension-Trainer Straps, Bracket Mount for Suspension-Training Equipment
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Exercise Machine Parts & Accessories › Exercise Machine Attachments
description: The TRX Training XMount is the ideal solution for creating a stable and secure anchor point for your TRX Home Suspension-Training Kit (sold separately). Designed with a unique X shape, this anchor allows you to hang multiple straps, enabling a full range of motion for an effective and versatile workout. The XMount attaches easily to your ceiling or wall, offering maximum stability for your suspension-training routine.Constructed from durable, powder-coated steel, the TRX XMount is built to withstand indoor and outdoor conditions. The plastic backing minimizes nicks and scratches, preserving the aesthetics of your installation area. Measuring compactly to fit any space, this mount includes 2 bolts for easy installation on any load-bearing wall or ceiling stud. Simply secure the bolts into a sturdy stud or beam, and you're ready to begin your training. Whether you’re a beginner or a seasoned athlete, the TRX XMount provides a solid foundation for all your suspension-training needs, making fit happen wherever you are.Move for the things that matter. TRX strength-training equipment is used by beginners, pro athletes, celebrity trainers, runners, yogis, cyclists, cross-trainers, service members, physical therapists, and combat athletes. With the TRX Training Club fitness app, you’ll have unlimited access to a virtual gym that includes live-streaming classes 7 days a week and hundreds of on-demand workouts, and you can even be matched with a personal trainer for a 1:1 training session. You can filter workouts by body part, workout type, duration, trainer, and fitness level. Whether you need yoga, HIIT, cardio, or strength-training equipment, we have what you need, when you need it. Join our loyal worldwide community and transform your entire body today.
features: HOME GYM EQUIPMENT: The TRX XMount anchor wall mount comes complete with 2 bolts for secure mounting. The unique X design allows you to hang the multiple straps in our TRX Home Suspension-Training Kit (sold separately).

SUSPENSION-STRAP ANCHOR: This is the ultimate anchor for a full range of motion. It attaches to your ceiling or wall for maximum stability. The durable powder-coated steel is indoor- and outdoor-ready, and the plastic backing reduces nicks and scratches.

EASY INSTALLATION: This TRX anchor kit mounts to any load-bearing wall or ceiling stud with the included bolts. It can be set up inside or outside to give you a custom hanging space that transforms anywhere into a resistance-training environment!

FOR ALL FITNESS LEVELS: TRX has a suspension-training system for everyone, and our exercise accessories can perform in the gym or at home. Whether you’re a seasoned pro, a beginner, or in between the two, we have the equipment to make fit happen.

YOUR TRIAL TO THE TRX TRAINING CLUB APP: Experience unlimited access to 500+ on-demand workouts: weight training, cardio, cross-training, sport athleticism, resistance and mobility training, and prehab and rehab. Find 100s of workouts for every goal! All workouts are guided by world-class certified TRX trainers.

KEY EXERCISES FOR SUCCESSFUL USE BY MEN AND WOMEN 
Exercise 1 
One foot in foot eradie(s) and centered with anchor point.

Drive heels down, lift hips up.
Lower hips toward ground with control.

Pull yourself into a balanced position with a lengthened torso.

Elbows bent and hands besides chest.

Pull body toward anchor point.

Extend arms in front of shoulders.
Bend elbows to lower the body.
Drive through palms, extending arms to return to start.
Exercise 6 
Position feet under anchor point and arms under shoulders.
Brace core, lift knees off the ground.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
THE HEAVY DUTY DOOR ANCHOR THAT OUTPERFORMS THE COMPETITION! 
Here at VPX Performance Sports, we are pro athletes & trainers. The body is our job & has been for over 15 years. We redesigned the everyday door anchor strap because we got tired of not being able to upload these door anchors properly, worrying about poor construction quality, & having them pull out of door jams too often. The result is our redesigned heavy duty door anchor that stays in any door jam - no matter its size! 
HEAVY DUTY CONSTRUCTION YOU CAN COUNT ON: Made of ballistic nylon with reinforced double stitched seams. Stainless steel D-ring with extra weave stitched edges. 
EXTRA LARGE STOPPER: We increased the size of the stopper to ensure that IT WILL NOT PULL OUT! We also made it thicker to ensure you have shock absorbing properties during any resistance band workout. This protects your door! 
WILL NOT SCRATCH OR DAMAGE YOUR DOOR: The dense foam padded door stopper will not scratch or damage your door - no matter the exercise. 
Fits Into Any Door Jam Safely! 
Oversized door stopper will not pull out & will not damage the door! Extra thick pad also provides cushioning during any workout. 
Reinforced In Every Way 
Made of ballistic nylon. Double stitched on all seams. Built to outlast the competition & give you years of unparalleled workout versatility! 
Clip It & Load It 
With our increased durability & features that most door anchors do not have, you can upload our door anchor & it will NOT pull out! 
Stainless Steel D-rings 
Will not bend under tension & provides you a durable ballistic nylon strap that takes years of abuse - no matter the workout you require!

How does the door anchor mechanism work? 
The door anchor mechanism uses a soft sponge material to securely anchor the straps to a door without causing any damage. This allows for a wide range of exercises to be performed using the door as an anchor point. 
Is it suitable for all fitness levels? 
The product description describes this as suitable for all fitness levels. This allows users to progress at their own pace as fitness improves. 
Can the length of straps be adjusted? 
Yes, the length of the straps can be adjusted using the one buckle system to provide different levels of resistance for a versatile full-body workout. 
How much weight can this straps support? 
The resistance trainer can support up to 500 pounds, as it is made of durable materials like high-quality polyester fiber and nylon that have undergone safety testing. 
Can the straps be used for yoga exercises? 
Absolutely! The straps are ideal for yoga, offering great support and enhancing your stretches. Whether you're a beginner or experienced, these straps will elevate your practice and help you achieve deeper poses.

title: URBNFit Gymnastic Rings - Bodyweight Workout and Strength Training Olympic Non-Slip Rings with Adjustable Straps for Crossfit and at Home Gym Workouts
inStockText: Only 15 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Sports › Other Sports › Gymnastics › Gym & Competition Equipment › Rings
description: WHY GYMNASTIC RINGS? URBNFit’s Gymnastic Rings combine cardio and strength training into one convenient, at-home workout. Burn fat, build muscle, gain core strength, and get the best upper body workout of your life from this easy to install workout tool.SCULPT LONG, LEAN MUSCLES Workouts with Gymnastic rings force you to target and add strain to muscle groups that you can’t hit from standard workouts or machines at the gym. Hit primary and secondary muscles with each positive and negative movement and sculpt the perfect gymnast’s body.HIGH QUALITY, HIGH PERFORMANCE, HIGH REWARD The rings are made from textured APS plastic that provides a more comfortable grip and eliminates slipping when your palms sweat. Once you secure the rings properly, they can hold your weight and much more, up to 1,000 pounds. The 17’ straps allow you set the rings to perfect height so you can tone your shoulders, chest, back, core, and legs.The URBNFit Gymnastic Rings Features: -Textured rings for comfortable, nonslip grip -Full bodyweight trainer -17’ straps -Locking buckles -Can hold up to 1,000 lbs when installed properly Installation instructions: Wrap the straps around an overhead and SECURE structure such as a pull-up bar, overhead beam, sturdy tree, monkey bars, or any structure that can hold and support your weight. The strap has two ends -- A pointed tip and a buckle. -Insert the end of the strap with the pointed tip through the ring, then insert the same tip into and pull it through the locking buckle. -Adjust the strap length to the desired height and start working out. It’s that easy!Let’s get you one step closer to your fitness goals! Click the BUY NOW button!
features: THE ULTIMATE BODYWEIGHT WORKOUT - Bodyweight training in the form of ring training develops upper body muscles, strengthens your core, and also improves mobility and flexibility. Bodyweight training is not only more effective than gym machines that only focus on limited muscle groups, it’s also more convenient. Just hang the rings on a suitably strong support and get an incredible workout from the comfort of your own home!

SET A NEW PERSONAL RECORD - Work out rings are more than an exercise accessory. Do Crossfit ring dips, pull-ups, muscle-ups, levers, iron crosses, and enjoy a bodyweight strength training that pushes you to engage multiple muscle groups at once.

COMFORTABLE NONSLIP GRIPS - The gymnastics rings have textured grips which are designed to eliminate slippage due to sweaty hands. Made with heavy-duty APS plastic, the rings can hold up to 1,000 lbs.

EASY TO INSTALL & SETUP - Wrap the straps around a secure bar, run the strap’s end through the ring and insert it into the locking buckle. Extra long 17-foot straps allow you to adjust the rings to the perfect length depending on your height and the workout you’re planning to do.

features: Reinforced Anchor Ceiling Mount – Able to support up to an amazing 750 lbs. this wall/ceiling mount anchor bracket is easy to install and is compatible with a wide range of personal and workout gear, working equipment, and accessories.
